reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very impressed for the price!
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love these bedside tables. They are so chic and sturdy, it has been a great addition to my bedroom. The drawer has lots of space and is able to fit everything I need it to. I love the compartment underneath to store extra blankets and hide my extension cords. My only complaint was that assembly took a lot longer than initially expected and the kit didn't include tools to assemble so make sure you have a screwdriver on hand! Overall, I think getting 2 bedside tables for this price is a steal when 1 can cost you upwards of $100. Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It was super cute and sturdy. The instructions are very detailed and everything is labeled so building it is super easy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not bad at all!
reviews.reviewText: So first, let me say that I was a bit nervous about purchasing these but the reviews are some of the most decent I’ve seen for nightstands PLUS I needed 2.Everything was packaged well in the box for both, the instructions were amazing. Like seriously, I got both cabinets together by myself in record time. I actually enjoyed putting them together.Pros: They’re pretty freaking sturdy, caught me by surprise honestly. Assembly was beyond easy, nice color, everything needed was there. The drawers fit correctly which is always a plus.Cons: There isn’t much to say that’s wrong. The back panel for one came chipped in the corner but it wasn’t a big deal for me as it wasn’t a huge chip. Thankfully I have my little handy drill I use (if you’re a woman reading this, don’t be afraid to get a drill. I walked into Home Depot and was like “I need a drill that’s not too heavy or heavy duty but gets jobs done” so if I can do it, so can you), some of the holes were like off in where they were suppose to be. So I’ve had to lightly use my drill to make holes but honestly you can use a screw driver too.Overall, I’m happy with my purchase. I rely heavily on reviews so I felt it was only right to do my part and write one for this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the 2-Tier Nightstand in White for my daughter's bedroom, and i love it.. It's not only a beautiful addition to her room but also incredibly functional. The drawer and storage shelf provide ample space to keep her bedtime essentials organized, and the sleek white design perfectly matches her decor. As a parent, I appreciate the sturdiness and quality of this nightstand, knowing it will last. It's a perfect fit for a child's bedroom and a great value for the price. I highly recommend this nightstand for anyone looking to enhance their child's bedroom with both style and functionality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great item great customer service.
reviews.reviewText: The side table is great. Its easy to assemble, the only thing is they didnt add instructions telling me to repeat the steps for the other side of the table, and I ended up not placing one of the drawer railings, but its an easy fix. It was also alright because the piece i was sent was defective! Fear not, as they swiftly and professionally handled the situation, sending me a new piece that had the wheel which i needed. Customer service was amazing in handling the issue, they told the manufacturer about the issue and got one headed my way after receiving a photo which confirmed the defect, and the piece which was needed. Overall, pretty damn good. Might want to assemble the stand on a high surface, since you'll be bent over working on it for some while. Hard on the back! The instructions were pretty clear at the very least. Huge thank you to this company!
